{"tid":1561162,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[不合作運動] 跳閘唔犯法方法!","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:46:20.000Z","uid":82312,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03d226945844addb7c6641b0e639e2d01dbd7a7b","tid":1561162,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"雖然跳閘只係民事法<br />\n但好多守規矩嘅香港人<br />\n都過唔到自己果關<br />\n<br />\n我研究過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跳閘其實唔犯法</span> <br />\n犯法嘅係唔比錢塔霸王車<br />\n所以大家唔想犯法又想出一分力<br />\n其實可以嘟完卡之後跳閘 只適用於舊閘機<br />\n法例冇限制人地點過果個閘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都比左錢狗鐵 有咩用?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲不法份子會因為你嘟左佢貪心地唔比錢入閘<br />\n<br />\n2.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有幾個嘟完但個閘機都唔郁<br />\n佢會卡左係到 後面再嘟會顯示 error<br />\n<br />\n3. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲人冇嘟到都入左 出閘時又要去站服處搞一輪 <br />\n做到同不合作運動一樣嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n4. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n引廢老藍絲住意 佢見你跳閘有機會咬住你唔放<br />\n當嘈到有好多人住意果時叫職員極你卡<br />\n一查 個廢老立即係咁多人面前炒車<br />\n<br />\n5.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等啲廢老唔肯定跳閘嘅人係咪真係冇拍卡<br />\n保護冇錢嘅學生哥<br />\n<br />\n咁做又合法 又做到各自爬山精神<br />\n一人出一分力"},{"pid":"bd720acdcbfec5cbb44aaf5b6c5a2ce60f92c8a2","tid":1561162,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e353e81dbe676b06acff16124c76a7733bfe05f9","tid":1561162,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"用綠卡啊唔該，慳得一蚊得一蚊，慳到既錢捐比義士"},{"pid":"cfbadcffa0236c795fe0b758712f21d2d29a72a6","tid":1561162,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ed3c99651366f49e075cd2db7713c416c3f42c","tid":1561162,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e353e81dbe676b06acff16124c76a7733bfe05f9","tid":1561162,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"用綠卡啊唔該，慳得一蚊得一蚊，慳到既錢捐比義士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"綠卡就係第二個方法<br />\n比啲唔怕比人捉嘅兄弟用<br />\n使用級數比較高"},{"pid":"61db8860b27db6a62330ff4159e8219369c8e0cd","tid":1561162,"uid":314132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:34:22.000Z","msg":"應該會留低記錄㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵你就好易㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479aff29c3a759b772e805b2a9b0b7583214f082","tid":1561162,"uid":82312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61db8860b27db6a62330ff4159e8219369c8e0cd","tid":1561162,"uid":314132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:34:22.000Z","msg":"應該會留低記錄㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵你就好易㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"搵到我然後點?<br />\n義士幫我打狗都唔怕<br />\n我怕佢搵到我比完錢之後跳閘?<br />\n<br />\n而且 唔用個人8達通 <br />\n佢點會花資源去搵一個唔犯法嘅人<br />\n除非得我一個咁做"},{"pid":"bd724b03dafe895c5d42390f27327fa6c540cb03","tid":1561162,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷消費港鐵商場仲有效 你一餐飯都50蚊！<br />\n當中有20蚊可能係租金！</span>"},{"pid":"cf75005fd304fa6d1f2bf0ccf35e9b812a14c135","tid":1561162,"uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"你跳唔緊要<br />\n一定要保護自己<br />\n我已經出post講過"}]}